  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TorqueL is a unique 2D \"rolling\" & \"extend\" platformer/action/puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Including total 50 chambers, 7 basic routes, and 1 secret route.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive music of product version composed by sanodg(Nobuyoshi Sano).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommended playing with Xbox 360 gamepad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Win10 + Xbox One Controller problems was fixed on Anniversary Update by pre-install driver renewed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250070/extras/8fae87b72596ca8dd8e55d43207bfcb1.avif?t=1728455512\" width=600 height=424 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TorqueL is a unique 2D \"rolling\" & \"extend\" platformer/action/puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Including total 50 chambers, 7 basic routes, and 1 secret route.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive music of product version composed by sanodg(Nobuyoshi Sano).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommended playing with Xbox 360 gamepad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Win10 + Xbox One Controller problems was fixed on Anniversary Update by pre-install driver renewed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250070/extras/8fae87b72596ca8dd8e55d43207bfcb1.avif?t=1728455512\" width=600 height=424 /></span></p>",
